%% NeMo Guardrails - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4/NeMo-Guardrails.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Server as NeMo Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant InputRails as Input Rails Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant Embeddings as Local Embedding Models<br/>(FastEmbed/spaCy)
    participant Jailbreak as Jailbreak Detection<br/>(YARA/API)
    participant LLM as Upstream LLM Server<br/>443/TCP or 8000/TCP
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails Engine<br/>(in-process)

    Note over Client,OutputRails: Flow 1: Guardrailed Chat Completion

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext, in-cluster)<br/>No Auth (platform-managed)

    Server->>InputRails: Apply input rails<br/>(in-process)

    InputRails->>Embeddings: Compute embeddings<br/>for similarity checks<br/>(in-process)
    Embeddings-->>InputRails: Embedding vectors

    InputRails->>Jailbreak: Check for jailbreak<br/>YARA rules (local) or<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (external API)
    Jailbreak-->>InputRails: Jailbreak check result

    alt Input rails BLOCK
        InputRails-->>Server: BLOCKED (safety violation)
        Server-->>Client: Guardrail rejection response<br/>HTTP 200 (with refusal message)
    else Input rails PASS
        InputRails-->>Server: PASSED

        Server->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (API Key)
        LLM-->>Server: Chat completion response

        Server->>OutputRails: Apply output rails<br/>(content safety, hallucination, SDD)
        OutputRails->>Embeddings: Validate output<br/>(in-process)
        Embeddings-->>OutputRails: Validation result

        alt Output rails BLOCK
            OutputRails-->>Server: BLOCKED (safety violation)
            Server-->>Client: Guardrail rejection response<br/>HTTP 200 (with refusal message)
        else Output rails PASS
            OutputRails-->>Server: PASSED
            Server-->>Client: Guardrailed response<br/>HTTP 200 JSON
        end
    end

    Note over Client,OutputRails: Flow 2: Guardrail-Only Check (No LLM Generation)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP (plaintext)

    Server->>InputRails: Apply input/output rails<br/>(in-process)
    InputRails->>Embeddings: NLP processing<br/>(spaCy, embeddings)
    Embeddings-->>InputRails: Processing result
    InputRails-->>Server: Check results<br/>(pass/block per rail)

    Server-->>Client: Guardrail check response<br/>HTTP 200 JSON
